<br>
Sorry, but it just disgusted me last night seeing an OGRE in Qeynos Hills and I could do <b>nothing</b> about it because he was green to me.<br>
<br>
At least lower the PvP+ level some, 6 is too exploitable, as bards get selo's at 5, and can train their arse off on people with no repercussions.<br>
<br>
Anyway, if anyone else feels this way, would you be willing to make a petition, /feedback, or spam the EQ boards ?<br>
<br>
 <p>Wang, Anonymous Gnome of Sullon Zek, <a href="http://pub70.ezboard.com/bscreamspvp">Anarchia</a><br>
