"Sorry, the law requires a five day waiting period... we've got to run a background check."<br>
"Aww, but I'm mad <i>now</i>." - Homer Simpson, buying a gun</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ugrinkle.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Grinkle</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Safehouse Supporter</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(7/9/01 9:19:15 am)</font><br>     <br>Community Supporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Would you prefer that people become PvP at level 2?</span><hr size=1> I'll send a single petition - spamming is bad for my quality of life!<br>
